node.text: Science Story is a collaboration between H&M and the brilliant thinkers, researchers and scientists that have devoted themselves to developing innovative, more sustainable textiles. Learn more about the ideas and materials behind the pieces with our creative advisor Ann-Sofie Johansson and concept designer Ella Soccorsi. The collection launches 18 March at hm.com (1 April in the 🇺🇸 & 🇨🇦). #HM #iamthefuture

node.text: For Molly & Joel, the creative couple behind #desmondanddempseyxHM Sunday is the most magical day of the week. It’s an in-between day where anything and everything can happen. It’s the day they would skype one another when they were living half a world apart (Canada 🌎🌏Australia ). It’s the day they fell in love and the day that inspired their pyjamas brand @desmondanddempsey 🌴 Molly and Joel now live in London where they hand paint all of their prints, but this collab (their first ever day wear collection) harkens back to summers spent in Australia.
